{"tid":1330102,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"逾30名7.1衝擊立法會示威者抵台灣尋庇護 傳已接觸陸委會","createTime":"2019-07-18T12:12:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-18T15:49:25.000Z","uid":68738,"like":24,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"a3979727bea1db4894aad55085e9327769c79de1","tid":1330102,"uid":68738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T12:12:04.000Z","msg":"7.1當晚示威者闖入及破壞立法會大樓，示威者或需面對警方追捕及法律責任。本報接獲可靠消息，逃往台灣的示威者人數逾30人，均為曾經參與7.1衝擊立法會行動的學生，他們事後沒有被捕，抵台後已接觸當地官方機構。<br />\n<br />\n自由亞洲電台亦有報道，有示威者已抵達台灣尋求庇護。報道中引述一名不願透露姓名的台灣律師，指衝擊立法會後，陸續有示威者抵台，正與陸委會接觸，尋求庇護。該名律師表示，由於該批示威者尚未被捕或檢控，衝擊時亦戴上口罩，難以證明自己曾經參與行動，因此他們要延長居台期限，技術上可能遇上困難。<br />\n<br />\n本報正就事件向保安局查詢。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190718/59838175\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190718%2F59838175&d=mJB0HZfowtkqKRKkSYSHExfhc2i76iEVsdTpjF8%2BTp8%3D&h=a4926d70\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190718%2F59838175&h=af55831c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190718/59838175</a>"},{"pid":"5e632e458da6d78ff4941116099cdfe0d6b29604","tid":1330102,"uid":92230,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T12:12:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔理你爭取咩先，你用暴力就一定錯？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1329924\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1329924</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"fffa399017ee4a97a0daf3f08846b7150ceb5805","tid":1330102,"uid":32511,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T12:12:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" clas